data.description: Absolutely beautiful Craftsman Style Home..This well-maintained home has 3 spacious bedrooms, 2.5 baths, HARDWOOD flooring on the main level, granite countertops, stainless appliances, with custom trim work and detailing throughout. The bright and sunny kitchen is open to the breakfast/family room. The family room is spacious with a fireplace and 9 ft ceilings. The master suite features a large walk-in closet, and the master bath boasts tile flooring, separate shower and jetted tub. Located in a wonderful neighborhood with amenities including clubhouse, POOL and sidewalks all within minutes from Jefferson/I-85. A beautiful level yard with a large front porch and fenced backyard are perfect for afternoon tea, grilling or entertaining.  This home is a MUST SEE and will not last long!!!
